      "writtenOn": "2026-07-07T14:40:46Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Thanks, Patrick. Agreed enabled\u003dfalse as the default is a poor choice.\nThe intent was to allow platforms to set their own defaults at build time via Meson options, but the option defaults themselves should be widely useful. I\u0027ll change the default for enabled to true (and revisit the others) so the system works\nout of the box without provisioning. Does that address your concern?",
      "parentUuid": "dd5c9641_669a2af9",
      "revId": "6b17f676c47ce3953befbd5430fec0303e808a07",
      "serverId": "adbd0a64-1f21-4d83-b585-671fe73cb6e4"
    },
